<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038388" n="143r"/>
<p>
<lb/>Spero Te accepisse <rs key="B_991170517038005501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> meam <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1717-11-19">19. <abbr>Nov.<hi rend="sup">bris</hi></abbr></date> scriptam, qua Tibi testatus
               <lb/>sum, me maximopere gavisurum, si contingeret, ut Te tanquam Collega
               <lb/>hic pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sente frui possem. Opto <add>eum in finem</add> ut vot<subst><del>a</del><add>is</add></subst> nostr<subst><del>a</del><add>is</add></subst> feli<subst><del>em habeant</del><add>x</add></subst> respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deat successus. Inclusam ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117498068" type="person">Fagnanum</rs> <rs key="B_991170517059405501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> rogo ut ad postam
               <lb/>deferri cures. Nullam hactenus accepi <rs type="letter">responsionem</rs><!-- brieftag, keine Antwort bekommen, vermutlich keiner hier, zu erfassen als nachgewiesener Brief--> ad <rs type="letter">litteras</rs><!-- brieftag Niklaus an Gadaldini--> quas
               <lb/>Te suadente ad Illum <abbr>D.</abbr> Secretarium <rs key="pers_DE-588-1222289342" type="person">Gadaldinum</rs> misi; si posses rescire
               <lb/>num ille acceperit eas nec ne, rogarem Te, ut me ejus rei certiorem
               <lb/>faceres, contentus enim ero, si scivero <rs type="letter">literas</rs><!-- brieftag, Kommentar dieser Brief ist nicht erhalten, leere brieftags löschen--> traditas fuisse. Rogavi
               <lb/>Te<del>ut</del> in dicta mea <rs key="B_991170517038005501" type="letter">epistola</rs>, ut mihi significare dignaveris, num ultim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
               <lb/>Tuam <rs key="B_991170517038205501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> ad me datam <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1717-11-12">12. 9bris</date> incluseris ei quam ad <abbr>D.</abbr> Mar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1038389" n="143v"/><lb break="no"/>chionem <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Polenum</rs> eadem die misisti, certam enim ob causam hoc maxime
               <lb/>scire laboro, quapropter si hac de re, unico quidem verbo,<del> respons</del> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>xime mihi responsum dare Tibi placebit, rem gratissimam facies.
            </p>
